TextEng: Who are you?
Who is this Maugrim?
Stand back! I'll have no tricks out of you!
Who you?
Who this Maugrim you talks of?
You stands back! No tricks from you!!
Are you sure of that?
You sure 'bout that?
I don't know if I like the way you're sizing me up...
Text: 당신이 나를 저렇게 훑어보는 게 마음에 들지 않는데요...

TextEng: Me not knows if me likes how you looking at me...
Text: 나 네가 나 쳐다보는 거 싫어...

TextEng: I am seeking a way to destroy the cult, and its leader.
Text: 사교와 그 지도자를 파괴할 방법을 찾고 있습니다.

TextEng: Me wants to destroy cult... and leader, too.
I'm the one asking the questions, here!
Me asks questions, not you!
How is it that you know all this?
Text: 어떻게 이 모든 걸 아는 거죠?

TextEng: How you knows all this stuff?
Text: 너 어떻게 이런 거 다 알아?

TextEng: I am an adventurer... exploring.
Me adventurer... me exploring.
Tell me who you are.
Tell me who you is.
What do you know about Maugrim? Where is he?
Text: 모그림에 대해 뭘 아나요? 그는 어디 있죠?

TextEng: What you knows 'bout Maugrim? Where he be?
Text: 너 모그림 뭐 알아? 그 어디 있어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Why are you here? Something seems very... odd.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 왜 여기 있는 거죠? 뭔가 매우... 이상한데요.

TextEng: What do you know about the Tower?
What you knows about Tower?
Forget it, I'm leaving.
Forget it, me going.
How do I know you're telling the truth?
Text: 어떻게 진실을 말하고 있다는 걸 알 수 있죠?

TextEng: How me know you tells the truth?
Text: 나 어떻게 너 진실 말하는지 알아?

TextEng: It's a trick, isn't it? The brazier will explode or something.
Text: 속임수죠? 화로가 폭발하거나 그럴 거 아니에요.

TextEng: Is trick, huh? Brazier go boom when me breaks it?
Text: 속임수지? 내가 부수면 화로 펑 터져?

TextEng: Why would I want to help you?
Why me wants to help you?
All right, I'll do it.
Okays, me do it.
Forget it... you can stay trapped here.
You forgets it... you stays here.
I want something now, in advance.
Me wants something now, before.
That does sound good...
That sounds good...
No, that's not enough.
No, is not enoughs.
I'm not talking about a reward.
Me not talk 'bout reward.
Not unless you make me a better offer.
Text: 더 나은 제안을 하지 않는 한 안 되죠.

TextEng: Only if you makes me really goods offer.
Text: 너 정말 좋은 제안 해야 해.

TextEng: I am sure.
Me sure.
Don't like it, huh? What are you going to do about it?
Text: 마음에 안 들어요? 그래서 어쩔 건데요?

TextEng: Not likes it, huh? What you do 'bout it?
I might change my mind.
Maybe me changes mind.
Changed my mind again... ha ha!
Ooops, change mind again! You stays, ha ha!
Text: 앗, 또 마음 바꿨어! 너 여기 있어, 하하!

TextEng: Why don't you destroy the brazier yourself?
Why you not destroys brazier yourself?
Text: 왜 너 직접 화로 안 부숴?

TextEng: Why were you imprisoned and not killed?
Why wizards not kills you?
Who are you? A wizard of the Brotherhood?
Who you be? Wizard of Brotherhood?
Prove you're not a cult follower. Tell me of their defenses.
Text: 사교 추종자가 아니라는 걸 증명하세요. 그들의 방어에 대해 말해 주세요.

TextEng: Prove you no cult follower. Tells me 'bout defenses.
Text: 너 사교 추종자 아닌 거 증명해. 방어 관련해서 말해 줘.

TextEng: I don't have any more questions.
Me have no more questions.
What do you mean?
What you means?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Why would Arklem have a non-wizard as an advisor?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 아클렘이 왜 마법사가 아닌 자를 조언자로 두었을까요?

TextEng: Are you telling me everything?
You tells me everything?
So you are evil like the rest of the Brotherhood.
So you is evil like the other wizards.
Text: 그럼 너도 다른 마법사들처럼 나쁜 놈이야.

TextEng: Why didn't you flee with Arklem, then?
Text: 그럼 왜 아클렘과 함께 달아나지 않았나요?

TextEng: Why you not flees with Arklem?
Text: 왜 너 아클렘이랑 같이 안 달아났어?

TextEng: His human wizards, you mean.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Primordial evil...? Such as a demon?
Of course it disturbs me!
Of course it disturb me!
No, not really.
No, it not disturbs me.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You are more than Arklem's advisor... you are not even human.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 당신은 아클렘의 조언자 이상이군요... 인간도 아니고.

TextEng: You don't sound like an advisor...
You not sound like advisor...
Such as?
Then you'll get no help from me.
Text: 그럼 나한테서 도움은 못 받을 거예요.

TextEng: Then me not helps you!
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Meaning you are not human at all, then.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그럼 당신은 인간이 전혀 아니라는 뜻이군요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lore]</Start> Meaning you would be sent back to your home plane? Inconvenient but not permanent.
Text: <StartCheck>[전승지식]</Start> 본래 차원으로 돌아가게 된다는 뜻인가요? 불편하긴 해도 영구적이진 않을 텐데.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lore]</Start> So you be sent back to planes? Is just inconvenient?
Text: <StartCheck>[전승지식]</Start> 그럼 본래 차원으로 돌아가요? 그냥 불편한 거예요?

TextEng: I don't understand...
Me not understand...
Very well... I'll destroy it.
Okay... me destroys it.
No.
I've had enough... you die now!
Me had enough... now you dies!
Text: 나 이제 지쳐... 이제 너 죽어!

TextEng: I'm not sure I should, actually.
Text: 사실 해야 할지 확신이 안 서요.

TextEng: Me not sure me should.
Text: 나 해야 할지 확실 안 해.

TextEng: Forget it... I'm not going to help you.
You forget it... me not helps you.
Text: 그냥 잊어... 나 너 안 도와.

TextEng: I'll do it.
Me will do it.
